# Work-in-progress: surface-syntax sketch, not type-checked.

fact ∀ a ∈ ℕ. a + 0 = a
fact ∀ a, b ∈ ℕ. a + b = b + a
fact ∀ a, b, c ∈ ℕ. (a + b) + c = a + (b + c)
fact ∀ a ∈ ℕ. a · 1 = a
fact ∀ a, b ∈ ℕ. a · b = b · a
fact ∀ a, b, c ∈ ℕ. (a · b) · c = a · (b · c)
fact ∀ a, b, c ∈ ℕ. a · (b + c) = a · b + a · c
